Steps.Message: Update at 20:52 - Hi, this is Kevin from the UK Power Networks messaging team. Thanks for your patience over tonight. Our engineers have been in contact with us to let us know that due to the extent of work required to repair the fault with the substation, the estimated timeframe to restore your power is now between 01:30 and 02:30. We're sorry this is taking longer than expected, and we'll continue to keep you up to date, but if any change to this time comes in from our staff I'll let you know as soon as we hear.

We became aware of a power cut at 17:41. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly.
Steps.Name: Power cut reported
